bf92c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.windowscentral.com/windows-10-october-2018-changelog</a><br />\n<br />\n最主要: system wide dark theme<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://www.windowscentral.com/sites/wpcentral.com/files/styles/xlarge/public/field/image/2018/07/rs5_fileexplorer-dark.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.windowscentral.com%2Fsites%2Fwpcentral.com%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fxlarge%2Fpublic%2Ffield%2Fimage%2F2018%2F07%2Frs5_fileexplorer-dark.jpg&h=b2ac939e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f91bf06526e784eee6f9738ae8a55667f37dadbb","tid":846242,"uid":168366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T14:22:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://3c.ltn.com.tw/news/34759\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F3c.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2F34759&d=%2BX40yYmwoEG9YEvn5HZpUY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=6fb92f2d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2F3c.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2F34759&h=767dded2\" target=\"_blank\">http://3c.ltn.com.tw/news/34759</a><br />\n<br />\n1.手機螢幕投放電腦<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XO303V2bQsg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXO303V2bQsg&d=%2BX40yYmwoEG9YEvn5HZpUY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=d8df1574\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XO303V2bQsg</a><br />\n新增「Your Phone App（你的手機）」的全新應用功能，讓 PC 電腦端的檔案文件內容，與用戶的iPhone、或 Android 手機無縫接軌，透過電腦螢幕出現的手機視窗進行操作，如:發送回覆手機收到的訊息、即時查看手機相簿照片等等。<br />\n<br />\n特別一提的是，微軟在這次發表會上，還特別展示了一項全新的應用功能。透過Your Phone App，讓用戶可以把Android手機螢幕畫面直接投放到 Windows 10 PC 電腦螢幕上。並預告之後還會提供功能更齊全的應用支援。至於iOS 部分，目前還沒有具體的細節。外媒推估在支援PC 電腦的應用功能性，Android 手機、iPhone手機將有所區別。<br />\n<br />\n手機照片同步到新版Windows 10 操作使用介紹影片：<br />\n(影片來源Windows官方YouTube頻道)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.全新的黑暗主題<br />\n<br />\n支援「夜間模式、或稱黑暗主題模式」的切換功能，並會擴展到檔案總管的視窗介面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/3c/page/2018/10/03/181003-34759-3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2F3c%2Fpage%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F181003-34759-3.png&h=aafb0734&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nWindows 10 2018十月更新版，新增黑暗主題模式。（圖翻攝自Zdnet）<br />\n<br />\n3.剪貼簿支援跨裝置<br />\n<br />\n可一次儲存多個項目在剪貼簿裡。利用快捷鍵組合：「Windows視窗」+ V鍵，即可快速啟動複製剪貼功能。另，可透過設定功能選單，選擇要不要自動同步。此外，還可透過同步功能，把同一個帳號所使用的剪貼簿文件檔案同步到另一台裝置上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/3c/page/2018/10/03/181003-34759-4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2F3c%2Fpage%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F181003-34759-4.jpg&h=dda30633&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n剪貼簿支援跨裝置。（圖翻攝自Computer World）<br />\n<br />\n4.新增智慧儲存功能 Storage Sense<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/3c/page/2018/10/03/181003-34759-5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2F3c%2Fpage%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F181003-34759-5.jpg&h=110906ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n透過新版系統內建的 Storage Sense 這項實用功能，可自動清理硬盤、釋放磁碟空間；並可與 OneDrive 雲端硬碟配合使用，除了釋放更多空間容量之外，還可管理清除不需要用到的文件，或是把 OneDrive 雲端文件永久保存在PC電腦端等。"},{"pid":"7fb9420bf77ddb9203561ed0b05bfbe4cc9d8ebd","tid":846242,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9461111a7f540057ae440f3ccfa7c5167ff92ce8","tid":846242,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef44cb9f00bbc9dab97b378986558b528de79501","tid":846242,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T12:08:37.000Z","msg":"恐怖的更新"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T12:40:06.000Z","msg":"有咩咁恐怖？你有用 windows 10 咩？有升 redstone 5 咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T16:17:01.000Z","msg":"有人送，可能會試下用"},{"pid":"e83e6b80841376ac478d5970022d626fcf5fd3bd","tid":846242,"uid":10009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f91bf06526e784eee6f9738ae8a55667f37dadbb","tid":846242,"uid":168366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T14:22:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://3c.ltn.com.tw/news/34759\" data-sr-url=\"http